CONTACT US
Here at JB Boondocks Bar & Grill we love to hear from our current customers and those thinking of visiting us for the very first time. Many of our customers have been dining with us since 1999. Why not join in on the fun and relax on the lake for dinner and cocktails.
We are always able to accomodate parties and small events, We always recommend if you are wanting reservations or planning an event that you call us as soon as you can. We book up very fast, so to get your request for reservations in please call us at (352) 324-3600.
If you have general questions about our restaurant, boat slip rentals or vacation apartment rentals feel free to send us a message using the form below or give us a call. Look forward to serving you soon.  ∼
Thank you.

About
Our History
Once the Palm Tree Harbour Fish Camp, “Mama B” purchased the Old Fish Camp in 1999. “Mama B” completely refurbished the bar, kitchen, docks and deck then naming the establishment “JB Boondocks Bar n’ Grill“. Since refurbishing JB Boondocks Bar & Grill located in Howey-in-the-Hills, the restaurant has become a favorite gathering place for both locals and visitors alike.
JB Boondocks is located directly on Little Lake Harris in Howey in the Hills. Want to come by boat? JB Boondocks boasts more than 20 boat slips, you can even park your seaplane. So come and enjoy our outdoor or indoor dining, entertainment and more.
It’s always been my dream to offer our visitors, friends and family a place to gather in friendship with great food, a relaxing atmosphere and a beautiful view.
Mama “B”
Founder
